  "description": "   \u003Cdiv class=\"descriptionContainer\"\u003E\n   \u003Cdiv class=\"pdpRow\"\u003E\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"productText\"\u003E\n     \u003Ch3\u003E\n      Simple Protection, Easy Storage\n     \u003C/h3\u003E\n     \u003Cp\u003E\n      This bag is made of high quality 1860D nylon. This fabric is strong, durable and water resistant. Thanks to the smooth surface dust and dirt cannot easily adhere and a wipe over with a damp cloth is often sufficient to make the bag look like new.\n     \u003C/p\u003E\n     \u003Ch3\u003E\n      Which Size\n     \u003C/h3\u003E\n     \u003Cp\u003E\n      Check our\n      \u003Ca href=\"https://www.cravenspeed.com/convertible-wind-deflector/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003E\n       Wind Deflector Product Page\n      \u003C/a\u003E\n      to find a wind deflector for your convertible. Once you've selected a deflector, the correct size bag is listed in the description. Alternatively, the table below shows which SKU uses which bag.\n     \u003C/p\u003E\n    \u003C/div\u003E\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"productGraphic\"\u003E\n     \u003Cimg alt=\"The Aperta wind deflector storage bag\" src=\"https://cravenspeed.com/product_images/uploaded_images/wind-deflector-bag-6.jpg\"\u003E\n    \u003C/div\u003E\n   \u003C/div\u003E\n   \u003Cdiv class=\"cs-table\"\u003E\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"cs-table-column\"\u003E\n        \u003Cdiv class=\"cs-column-header\"\u003ES\u003C/div\u003E\n        \u003Cdiv class=\"cs-table-cell\"\u003EOTS-AH143\u003C/div\u003E\n        \u003Cdiv class=\"cs-table-cell\"\u003EOTS-AH314\u003C/div\u003E\n        \u003Cdiv class=\"cs-table-cell\"\u003EOTS-AH317\u003C/div\u003E\n        \u003Cdiv class=\"cs-table-cell\"\u003EOTS-AH293\u003C/div\u003E\n        \u003Cdiv class=\"cs-table-cell\"\u003EOTS-AH933\u003C/div\u003E\n        \u003Cdiv class=\"cs-table-cell\"\u003EOTS-AE665\u003C/div\u003E\n        \u003Cdiv class=\"cs-table-cell\"\u003EOTS-AH981\u003C/div\u003E\n        \u003Cdiv class=\"cs-table-cell\"\u003EOTS-